      Press release
    </span>
  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    United Kingdom and Canada announce recipient of first Media Freedom Award
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">Belarusian Association of Journalists recognized for commitment to journalistic ethics and principles in the face of increased crackdowns on media in Belarus.</p>

  </div>
</div>

<div class="govuk-grid-row">
  <div class="metadata-logo-wrapper">
